#lg B	sa-jara



@(1-12=c40808.B.B.1) 
$ (1 line fragmentary)
$ (1 line unclear)
There he is, standing at our mother's gate, while I am rushing around in excitement. There he is standing at @wDN{Ningal's} gate, while I am rushing around in excitement. Oh that someone would tell my mother! May our neighbour come to sprinkle water on the floor! Oh that someone would tell my mother @wDN{Ningal}! May our neighbour come to sprinkle water on the floor: the fragrance of her dwelling is pleasant, and her words are delightful.

@(13-20=c40808.B.B.13) My lord is perfect for the holy embrace. @wDN{Ama-ušumgal-ana}, the son-in-law of @wDN{Suen}, Lord @wDN{Dumuzid}, is perfect for the holy embrace. @wDN{Ama-ušumgal-ana}, son-in-law of @wDN{Suen}, my lord: how pleasing is your lavishness, and how sweet-tasting are your green plants from the plain! @wDN{Ama-ušumgal-ana}, how pleasing is your lavishness, and how sweet-tasting are your green plants from the plain!

